* Range\nChecking
** Purpose
***_ Catches out-of-bound values
***_ Data entry errors
***_ System glitches
***_ Integration issues
** Operators
***_ BETWEEN clause
***_ Comparison operators (>=, <=)
***_ current_date() for date limits
** Pipeline Expectations
***_ Python: @dp.expect_or_fail
***_ SQL: CONSTRAINT + BETWEEN
***_ Numeric, date & complex rules
** Delta Lake CHECK Constraints
***_ ALTER TABLE ADD CONSTRAINT
***_ Enforced at write time
***_ Combined conditions
** Business Rules
***_ Multi-condition constraints
***_ Tiered discount rules
***_ Cross-column validation
@endmindmap
